## 3. API Request Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant NextJS as Next.js<br/>API Routes
    participant Express as Express<br/>Backend :3001
    participant Prisma
    participant DB as SQLite/PG

    Note over Browser,DB: User Authentication Flow
    Browser->>NextJS: POST /api/frontend/auth/login
    NextJS->>Express: POST /auth/login
    Express->>Prisma: findUnique user
    Prisma->>DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE email=?
    DB->>Prisma: User record
    Prisma->>Express: User object
    Express->>Express: bcrypt.compare(password)
    Express->>Express: jwt.sign({userId, role})
    Express->>NextJS: {token, user}
    NextJS->>Browser: Login response

    Note over Browser,DB: Asset Publishing Flow
    Browser->>NextJS: POST /api/frontend/assets
    NextJS->>Express: POST /assets
    Express->>Prisma: create asset
    Prisma->>DB: INSERT INTO assets...
    DB->>Prisma: Asset created
    Prisma->>Express: Asset object
    Express->>Express: Calculate GDI Score
    Express->>OpenAI: Request GDI
    OpenAI->>Express: GDI Score
    Express->>Prisma: update gdiScore
    Express->>NextJS: {asset, gdiScore}
    NextJS->>Browser: Publish success
```

