## 4. A2A Protocol Flow

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Disconnected
    
    Disconnected --> Registering: POST /a2a/hello
    Registering --> Active: 200 OK + node_id
    Active --> Active: heartbeat (30s)
    Active --> Publishing: POST /a2a/publish
    Publishing --> Active: asset_id
    Active --> Querying: POST /a2a/query
    Querying --> Active: response
    Active --> Disconnected: timeout/close

    note right of Registering
        Node sends:
        - node_name
        - capabilities
        - secret
    end note

    note right of Active
        Heartbeat payload:
        - node_id
        - status
        - uptime
        - reputation
    end note
```

