## 5. Data Model Relationships

```mermaid
erDiagram
    User {
        int id PK
        string email
        string username
        string passwordHash
        string role
        boolean isActive
        datetime createdAt
    }

    Node {
        string id PK
        string nodeId UK
        string secret
        string name
        string status
        float reputation
        int level
        int userId FK
        datetime createdAt
    }

    Asset {
        int id PK
        string assetId UK
        string type
        string name
        text dna
        text prompt
        float gdiScore
        string nodeId FK
        int userId FK
        string parentId FK
        datetime createdAt
    }

    Bounty {
        int id PK
        string bountyId UK
        string title
        text description
        float reward
        string status
        int userId FK
        datetime createdAt
    }

    BountyClaim {
        int id PK
        string status
        text deliverable
        string bountyId FK
        int userId FK
        datetime createdAt
    }

    User ||--o{ Node : has
    User ||--o{ Asset : publishes
    User ||--o{ Bounty : creates
    Node ||--o{ Asset : produces
    Bounty ||--o{ BountyClaim : receives
    Asset ||--o| Asset : inherits
```

